unittitle_ssm: Socialist Party (U.S.) Membership Index Card Collection
abstract_ssm: The Socialist Party (U.S.) was founded in 1901, bringing together moderate socialists from the Social Democratic Party, and dissident members of the Socialist Labor Party.  The Socialist Party (U.S.) Membership Index Card Collection consists of index cards listing the names and addresses of Socialist Party members by state.
